data.description: This Elk Grove Subdivision home on the outskirts of Bozeman, is an absolute must see. Inviting and custom touches around every corner, this 4 bedroom (plus office and bonus room) and 3.5 bath home provides relaxation and serenity throughout. With over 3400 SQFT there's room for ALL! Walking in you are greeted with a wide entryway and bright office, continuing on are the living room and entertaining areas leading you into the custom kitchen. Offering updated appliances and custom cabinetry. The East side of the main level has all you need or entertaining guests and/or quietly enjoying your morning coffee! Main level also has the primary suite, a laundry room, powder room, plenty of storage and a true 2 car garage. The upstairs provides 3 bedrooms (all with incredible views), a massive bonus room and 2 bathrooms. Walking outside into the fully fenced yard, backed up by HOA maintained open space, transports you from your busy days. A paver patio, pergola and lovely gas powered fireplace are just some of the attributes. The mature landscaping in the front and back of the home, adds to the privacy and peace abound. This subdivision has established trail systems and a lovely park with a pond that provide a true community feel. Welcome home, schedule your showing today!
